## Agent learning logs → moved to `carnatic/LEARNINGS.md`

The dated learning-log entries (formerly ~450 lines here) now live in
`carnatic/LEARNINGS.md` to keep this operating manual lean. **Do not read that
archive at session start** — recall from it only when relevant:

```bash
grep -in "<topic>" carnatic/LEARNINGS.md
```

**Appending a new entry** (end of session): add one terse dated line to your
agent's subsection in `carnatic/LEARNINGS.md`, not here.
Format: `- YYYY-MM-DD: <one plain-prose sentence>`.
